  "description": "The figure-eight has a single crossing point where the two loops touch. This preset lives at that crossing — tangle 0.55, entrain 0.4 — close enough to feel the topology but not fully knotted. LFO1 sweeps the tangle back and forth so the crossing point is approached and retreated from continuously.",
